      "bullets": [
        "Practitioners use Ollama and Continue with Qwen2.5-Coder-32B or DeepSeek-Coder-V2 to replace Claude and GPT-4 for local development.",
        "Running 30B+ models at usable speeds (>20 tok/s) requires high-end hardware like Apple M-series Max/Ultra or NVIDIA RTX 4090 GPUs.",
        "Local models excel at inline autocomplete, but Claude 3.5 Sonnet still outperforms them on complex, multi-file codebase reasoning tasks."
      ]
    },
